1	Start the game



2	Deal the hands
	Deal cards to player 1
	deal cards to player 2


3 Play the tricks
	Player 1 selects their card to play
		Card is played into the center facedown (Player 2 is blind)
	Player 2 selects their card to play
	Cards in play are flipped over revealing values
	Player with the highest value card wins the trick
		Point is asigned to the player's trick total
Repeat this step until all hands are empty

4) End of hand
	assign a point to the player with the most tricks hand count
		Reset trick points
	Reset deck
go to 2)

2-If> If there are not 6 cards left in step 2
		End the game
		announce the player with the most hand points as the winner





